data.meta_description: MarkLogic is a database designed for NoSQL speed and scale, without sacrificing the enterprise features required to run mission-critical, operational applications. The marklogic-geotools-plugin provides direct read-only access to a MarkLogic database via the GeoTools library.  - marklogic-geotools-plugin/LICENSE.txt at master · marklogic-community/marklogic-geotools-plugin
